18
00:01:01,565 --> 00:01:03,740
So at a very basic level,

19
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:06,605
a table is a collection of rows and columns.

20
00:01:06,605 --> 00:01:13,055
A relational database is a digital database based on the relational model of data.

21
00:01:13,055 --> 00:01:16,010
A software system used to maintain

22
