relational databases is a relational database management system or RDBMS.

23
00:01:22,805 --> 00:01:26,360
The relational model and the relational database were invented at

24
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:30,290
IBM and by Edgar Codd in the late 60's and early 70's.

25
00:01:30,290 --> 00:01:34,805
It is a digital database that is modeled after relational model of data.

26
00:01:34,805 --> 00:01:40,475
The software system to maintain a relational database is referred to as an RDBMS.

27
00:01:40,475 --> 00:01:42,170
So just a note here,

28
